SD-RFI-001,24-Mar-26,,,B1-B4 Structural Package Conflict,Significant structural design update received; Technical Office found dimensional and spatial clashes between revised columns and slab openings.,Consultant suggested manual combination of legacy column design with new slab design; contractor rejected due to design liability risk.,Production halted until the 30-Apr-2026 consolidated package reconciled legacy columns with new slab design.
SD-RFI-002,24-Mar-26,,,As-Built Column Conflict / B1-B4,March update conflicted with as-built reality because columns had already been cast based on the 27-Oct-2025 baseline.,Unified IFC required from the consultant; contractor position maintained that design responsibility must not transfer to contractor.,30-Apr-2026 package acknowledged fixed vertical elements and reconciled slabs with existing columns.
